

{"id":6296,"date":"2024-03-14T14:43:34","date_gmt":"2024-03-14T07:43:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6296"},"modified":"2024-03-20T09:06:58","modified_gmt":"2024-03-20T02:06:58","slug":"co-the-can-hoi-phuc-trong-bao-lau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/co-the-can-hoi-phuc-trong-bao-lau\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c trong bao l\u00e2u?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-6450\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_8037-1-1024x732.jpg\" alt=\"c\u01a1 th\u1ec3\" width=\"1024\" height=\"732\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_8037-1-1024x732.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_8037-1-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_8037-1-768x549.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_8037-1-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_8037-1-2048x1463.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t quy lu\u1eadt c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c, v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y\u00a0 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 7 ti\u1ebfng m\u1ed7i \u0111\u00eam. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Theo d\u00f5i ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, h\u00e3y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. L\u1eafng nghe v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, h\u00e3y cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 l\u1eafng nghe c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/thong-tin-ve-chuoi-phong-tap-the-new-gym\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Email: cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helv